summary: "Teen J News" is a weekly, offbeat look at what's happening in the world of teen journalism. The first issue was published on June 6, 1995. It was the first edition of the journal, published under the name Teen J. News. In the second edition, it was re- published with the title "Teen Journal" on July 1, 1996.
